36:43.952 --> 36:47.122
♪ Don't be so thoughtful,
just show me the money ♪

36:47.122 --> 36:49.916
[ Siren wailing ]

36:49.916 --> 36:53.378
♪♪

36:53.378 --> 36:56.631
[ Breathing heavily ]

36:56.631 --> 36:59.217
[ Chuckles ]

36:59.217 --> 37:01.302
Let's go.

37:01.302 --> 37:03.179
You really
don't wanna do this.

37:03.179 --> 37:04.472
Screw that.

37:04.472 --> 37:05.890
If I'm going back,

37:05.890 --> 37:07.976
I want to add "kicking your ass"
to the list of charges.

37:07.976 --> 37:11.688
[ Grunting ]

37:11.688 --> 37:13.565
You were saying?

37:13.565 --> 37:15.066
[ Breathing heavily ]

37:18.737 --> 37:20.905
[ Exhales sharply ]
Hey.
I was hoping I'd catch you.

37:20.905 --> 37:22.240
You know what?
It's been a really long day,

37:22.240 --> 37:24.451
and I'm not sure how much more
bad news I can handle right now.

37:24.451 --> 37:26.703
What if it's good news?
Is this a joke?

37:26.703 --> 37:29.122
I convinced my boss
to a cut good deal for Tyler.

37:29.122 --> 37:30.540
Really?

37:30.540 --> 37:32.083
He won't be charged
as an adult.

37:32.083 --> 37:34.335
He'll serve six months
in juvie,

37:34.335 --> 37:36.004
then probation
till he turns 18.

37:36.004 --> 37:37.547
That's a good deal.

37:37.547 --> 37:39.090
I know
you think I'm a rookie

37:39.090 --> 37:40.550
who doesn't have the experience
to do the job,

37:40.550 --> 37:42.218
but you should maybe
give me a break.

37:42.218 --> 37:44.387
I actually think we're working
toward the same goal.

37:44.387 --> 37:46.055
Just coming at it
from different angles.

37:46.055 --> 37:49.434
Well, um, I appreciate
you making this happen.

37:49.434 --> 37:51.227
I appreciate
you convincing me.

37:51.227 --> 37:52.854
[ Chuckles ]

37:52.854 --> 37:54.439
Good night.

37:54.439 --> 37:57.984
♪♪

37:57.984 --> 38:00.945
So, I've been, uh ‐‐
I've been thinking about

38:00.945 --> 38:02.781
your offer to do the show
with me.

38:02.781 --> 38:04.908
Really?
Yeah.

38:04.908 --> 38:06.785
Look,
if you can promise me

38:06.785 --> 38:08.787
that I'll have full control
over the pieces of my life

38:08.787 --> 38:10.955
that we expose,
then...yeah.

38:10.955 --> 38:11.956
I'll do it.

38:11.956 --> 38:13.333
Cut.

38:13.333 --> 38:14.584
What's the problem?

38:14.584 --> 38:16.753
It sounds fake.
What does?

38:16.753 --> 38:18.963
<i>You.</i> Listen, if you want people
to watch this show,

38:18.963 --> 38:20.757
you gotta sound real.

38:20.757 --> 38:22.008
You gotta be real.

38:22.008 --> 38:23.259
Yeah,
listen to her, Aaron.

38:23.259 --> 38:24.761
Your mama's
the queen of "real."

38:24.761 --> 38:26.638
Can I get
a touch‐up?!

38:26.638 --> 38:28.306
Let's get a touch‐up.

38:28.306 --> 38:30.391
♪ Feel the light ♪
[ Sighs ]

38:30.391 --> 38:32.393
♪ Feel the light ♪

38:32.393 --> 38:35.480
Lucy: You sure
I can't make you something?

38:35.480 --> 38:37.315
I'm not really hungry.

38:37.315 --> 38:38.942
♪♪

38:38.942 --> 38:41.945
Today sucked.
Yeah.

38:41.945 --> 38:43.822
Big time.

38:43.822 --> 38:48.952
♪ I'm with you by your side ♪

38:48.952 --> 38:50.829
♪ By your side ♪
Thank you.

38:50.829 --> 38:51.871
For...?

38:51.871 --> 38:53.790
Everything.

38:53.790 --> 38:56.000
For all your help.

38:56.000 --> 38:58.628
For this bed.

38:58.628 --> 39:00.964
For getting justice
for Becca.

39:00.964 --> 39:03.299
You did that.

39:03.299 --> 39:05.885
♪ I know it gets heavy ♪

39:05.885 --> 39:08.304
And thanks for helping me
leave it all behind,

39:08.304 --> 39:09.973
because if
it weren't for you,

39:09.973 --> 39:12.976
I probably would have ended up
like Becca eventually.

39:12.976 --> 39:17.021
Well, you don't have to
worry about that anymore.

39:17.021 --> 39:18.898
You're safe.

39:18.898 --> 39:20.650
♪♪

39:20.650 --> 39:23.236
Do you wanna talk about
what you went through

39:23.236 --> 39:25.071
when you were living
on the street?

39:25.071 --> 39:27.866
Um, not now,
if that's okay.

39:27.866 --> 39:29.659
Yeah, we don't have to
talk about it now.

39:29.659 --> 39:31.369
You don't have to
talk about it with me.

39:31.369 --> 39:32.871
You know,
but at some point,

39:32.871 --> 39:36.666
you might wanna
talk to someone...

39:36.666 --> 39:38.167
before it sneaks up
on you.

39:38.167 --> 39:40.461
♪ Feel the light ♪

39:40.461 --> 39:42.046
I will.

39:42.046 --> 39:44.048
I promise.

39:44.048 --> 39:45.842
Okay.

39:45.842 --> 39:48.177
Good night.

39:48.177 --> 39:50.471
Do you want this open
or closed?

39:50.471 --> 39:52.515
Closed, please.

39:52.515 --> 39:55.393
♪ I'm with you by your side ♪
Sweet dreams.

39:55.393 --> 39:58.563
♪ By your side ♪

39:58.563 --> 40:00.857
♪ I'm by your side ♪

40:00.857 --> 40:02.275
You wanted to talk?

40:02.275 --> 40:05.695
Um, actually,
I‐I was hoping for

40:05.695 --> 40:07.572
more of a do‐over.

40:07.572 --> 40:11.075
Um...I don't like
how I handled it

40:11.075 --> 40:13.286
when you told me
you were pregnant.

40:13.286 --> 40:15.914
Yeah, you didn't handle it.
You didn't do anything.

40:15.914 --> 40:17.957
You just stood there.

40:17.957 --> 40:19.292
I know.

40:19.292 --> 40:23.546
Um, I can only plead
temporary stupidity

40:23.546 --> 40:28.259
and throw myself
at your mercy.

40:28.259 --> 40:29.844
♪♪

40:29.844 --> 40:31.220
Forgive me.

40:31.220 --> 40:32.889
Get up.

40:32.889 --> 40:36.100
So, am I forgiven?

40:36.100 --> 40:37.685
Yes.
Yes, get up.

40:37.685 --> 40:42.315
Look, look,
um, I'm here, okay?

40:42.315 --> 40:45.234
I‐I'm ready to listen.
I'm ‐‐ I'm ready to talk.

40:45.234 --> 40:47.487
I'm ready to do
whatever it is you need.

40:47.487 --> 40:50.323
I need you
to understand something.

40:50.323 --> 40:52.158
I made my peace

40:52.158 --> 40:54.327
with not being able
to get pregnant again,

40:54.327 --> 40:58.957
and so I never even
allowed myself to fantasize...

40:58.957 --> 41:01.084
♪ By your side ♪

41:01.084 --> 41:03.795
♪ I'm by your side ♪

41:03.795 --> 41:06.589
I'm gonna have
this baby.

41:06.589 --> 41:08.591
[ Exhales sharply ]

41:08.591 --> 41:09.884
♪ I'm by your side ♪

41:09.884 --> 41:12.011
Well, then, um...

41:12.011 --> 41:16.766
you and I are going to make
a kick‐ass team

41:16.766 --> 41:19.227
because we're gonna fight
every day

41:19.227 --> 41:20.770
to make sure
that this baby

41:20.770 --> 41:22.772
gets to live
in a much better world

41:22.772 --> 41:24.273
than the one
that exists right now.

41:24.273 --> 41:26.359
That's a good answer.

41:26.359 --> 41:28.987
[ Siren wails in distance,
horn honks ]

41:28.987 --> 41:30.989
[ Sniffles ]

41:30.989 --> 41:34.033
♪ So open up your eyes ♪

41:34.033 --> 41:35.994
There we go.

41:35.994 --> 41:37.495
The sommelier
recommended this red.

41:37.495 --> 41:39.163
Sounds fancy.

41:39.163 --> 41:41.624
Yeah. Full disclosure, it was
the guy at the liquor store.

41:41.624 --> 41:43.126
But he just said
everyone's buying this bottle.

41:43.126 --> 41:44.627
[ Chuckles ] Thanks.

41:44.627 --> 41:45.920
A toast.

41:45.920 --> 41:48.089
To finally
being able to exhale.

41:48.089 --> 41:50.174
Mm.
Can we?

41:50.174 --> 41:51.551
Yes.

41:51.551 --> 41:55.805
Jason is behind bars
for eight years,

41:55.805 --> 41:57.348
you have a divorce hearing
set for next month,

41:57.348 --> 41:59.600
and when your future
ex‐husband finally gets out,

41:59.600 --> 42:01.019
we'll get
a restraining order.

42:01.019 --> 42:02.270
Mm.

42:02.270 --> 42:04.814
I really appreciate you
helping me through this mess.

42:04.814 --> 42:06.816
Anytime.

42:06.816 --> 42:10.028
Though, I confess,
I do find myself wondering

42:10.028 --> 42:13.197
if there isn't yet another
crazed lunatic of a husband

42:13.197 --> 42:15.575
from your checkered past
lurking around out there.

42:15.575 --> 42:16.868
There isn't.
[ Chuckles ]

42:16.868 --> 42:18.703
What a relief.
Evil twin?

42:18.703 --> 42:20.163
Triplets.
Is that a problem?

42:20.163 --> 42:22.206
Triplets
I can work with.

42:22.206 --> 42:23.082
[ Glasses clink ]

